               <p>Fourth Count. Laying them to be the property of certain persons to the Jurors unknown. </p>
               <p>(The indictment was opened by Mr. Vaillant, and the case by Mr. Knowlys.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17991030-2-person66">
